steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Input the New Item name
Select Job Type on NewJobPage
Click 'OK' button
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Get Header
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
click 'My Views' link from side menu
Click to create a new View
Set a View Name
Select View Type and click 'Create'
Get Header
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
click 'My Views' link from side menu
Click on the last created view name 'View1CKdoq94' button on the MyViews page
Click on the 'Delete View' button on the side menu
Click on the 'Yes' button on the DeletePage
Check if view is shown in the View Bar
